Why can't they hear me?

144
00:09:45,204 --> 00:09:47,200
- Who?
- Them!

145
00:09:47,304 --> 00:09:49,807
- Ok, tell me what's happening.
- Tell me what's happening.

146
00:09:49,907 --> 00:09:51,706
