147
00:09:51,809 --> 00:09:56,103
- You mean your body's being moved.
- No! I'm running. My feet are bleeding.

148
00:09:56,208 --> 00:10:00,403
I cut them trying to escape.
I... but I didn't want to escape.

149
00:10:00,505 --> 00:10:03,801
